title: Tin Foil Hat #71: Deep Underground Military Bases with Bert Kreischer
description:
Welcome to another interesting episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome to the bunker the Machine, Bert Kreischer. This episode we discuss....
1) Bert's new special
2) the Oscars
3)Weaponized Poliitical Correctiness
4) The World of F.F's
5) National Reconnaissance Office,
6) Deep Black Programs
7) Casa Blanca" (White House)
8)Raven Rock Mountain Complex​
9)Cheyenne Mountain
10) ​​Dulce, New Mexico
11) Project Plowshare
12) The Denver International Airport (DIA)
13)Underwater base off the Coast of Malibu
14)Ryan Time Tavels to Van Nuys Blvd 1979
Thank you for all of your support. For more Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli check out Patreon.com/TinFoilHat
